mprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" title=\"大哥咱能少系几个扣子嘛？\" alt=\"大哥咱能少系几个扣子嘛？\" src=\"/Uploads/remoteImage/66171415074308.jpg\" _size=\"112841\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />大哥咱能少系几个扣子嘛？</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">好的，扯的有点远……下面回到正题，页面拉到中间，将需要的颜色和号码加入购物车，这里选择藏青色（NAVY）XS码：<br style=\"outline:0px;\" /></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" alt=\"潮牌直邮 ReggieShop\" src=\"/Uploads/remoteImage/35621415074308.jpg\" _size=\"182922\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 20px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" /></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">如果没有别的需求，直接点击下面红色按钮进入购物车结算即可。<br style=\"outline:0px;\" /></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" alt=\"潮牌直邮 ReggieShop\" src=\"/Uploads/remoteImage/60231415074309.jpg\" _size=\"311857\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 20px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" /></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">第一次购物的话，不能直接成为会员，需要购买后才能注册，所以这里直接拉到页面下方填写相应信息。前面也看到了，这家只是日本地方上的小店，也没有成熟的电子商务系统，快递单还是由店主或者店员手写，所以咱们<span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">直接上繁体中文</span>即可！是不是爽到爆！<br style=\"outline:0px;\" /></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">其实简体中文也可以，就是让他们的电脑可能出乱码，影响发货速度。</p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">常来的话记得注册会员换取积分，比如这件5万日元的西服大概可以折合4000多分，下次直接省下200多元，更加实惠啦！</p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><br style=\"outline:0px;\" /><img itemprop=\"image\" alt=\"潮牌直邮 ReggieShop\" src=\"/Uploads/remoteImage/3921415074309.jpg\" data-ke-src=\"http://pn.zdmimg.com/201411/02/5455ec16ba729.jpg\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 20px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" /></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">邮寄方式没什么好说的，海外用户就选择<span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">EMS</span>吧！<br style=\"outline:0px;\" /></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" title=\"EMS国际包邮还是比较爽的！\" alt=\"