px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />添加新收获地址</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">④需要注意的是，虽然网站贴心地提供了中文页面，但地址的填写仍旧只支持<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">英文或拼音</strong>输入（中文符号也不支持）。寄往国内地址的话，小编<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">建议大家都填写拼音地址，并且按照中文语序填写即可</strong>。例如，<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">北京市朝阳区值得买路月光小区88号</strong>，则填写<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">BeiJingShi，ChaoYangQu，ZhiDeMai Lu，YueGuang XiaoQu，88 hao</span></strong> 即可。 </p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">以我们海淘直邮的经验，电话号码经常会在包裹单上消失，建议<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">在地址栏里填写电话号码</strong>，方便派件员联系。填写完毕，点击“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">保存</span></strong>”即可。</p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bee160e9a.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"8340\" alt=\"填写收货地址\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />填写收货地址</span></p><h3 style=\"outline:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;color:#333333;line-height:26px;\">2.选择默认运送方式</h3><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">选择“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">首选项</span></strong>”里的“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">优选运送方式</span></strong>”，SHOPBOP网目前提供三种运送方式，选项中的命名比较类似，不好分辨，以下三张图示，按顺序对应即可；包括<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">Shopbop Global</strong>、<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">DHL/UPS 国际快递</strong>以及<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">USPS国际邮政</span></strong>，优缺点对比如下方表格，大家按需选择即可。<br style=\"outline:0px;\" /></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bee1e25ca.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"16558\" alt=\"选择送货方式\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />选择送货方式</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bee27375a.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"223401\" alt=\"送货方式对比\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />送货方式对比</span></p><h3 style=\"outline:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;color:#333333;line-height:26px;\">3.填写支付信息</h3><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">①SHOPBOP网不仅支持双币信用卡，还可使用国内<span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">单币银联卡</span>，但仅支持<span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">62开头</span>的信用卡。<br style=\"outline:0px;\" /></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bee7106b0.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"9186\" alt=\"多种支付方式\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />多种支付方式</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bee80cd70.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"6196\" alt=\"银联支付\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />银联支付</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">②点击“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">账户信息</strong>”里的“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">信用卡</span></strong>”，再点击“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">添加新卡</span></strong>”，进入填写页面。</p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bee5823d8.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"1364\" alt=\"添加信用卡\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />添加信用卡</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">③按提示要求填写信用卡信息以及账单地址。账单地址若为之前填写的收货地址，则可直接选择，若否，则选择“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">添加新账单地址</span></strong>”，在弹出的下拉页面里填写即可，规则与填写收货地址相同。填写完毕，点击“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">保存</span></strong>”即可。</p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bee87f83e.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"16376\" alt=\"添加账单地址\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />添加账单地址</span></p><h2 style=\"outline:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:18px;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;color:#333333;line-height:26px;\">三.SHOPBOP网购物及支付流程</h2><h3 style=\"outline:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;color:#333333;line-height:26px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;font-size:14px;\">1.商品分类</span><br style=\"outline:0px;\" /></h3><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;\">大家可以按照新款上市、品牌分类、精选推荐、折扣促销、造型杂志的主题来挑选，即便不买，来看看最新潮流走向，或是学习下搭配造型都是不错的。或者以服饰、鞋履、包袋、配饰的分类来选购，更加直观；每个分类底下又有更详细的分类，非常贴心。</span><br style=\"outline:0px;\" /></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-fami